 to give up their essence for me) without any real difficulty. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.leagueofhonour.com/images/members/oligith.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Master Koada'dal Phantasmist of the 61st Circle<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>  Elf of Many Faces</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=425188">Equipment</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> | <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/lsteim/OgHist.html">Stories</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=angeliqueie>Angeliqueie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mirror Mirror<br>on the Wall </span><br>  Posts: 34<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/9/03 12:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=194.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Non agnostic enchanters</span><hr size=1> I actually did that... and if I was young enough I probably would reroll, at lower levels it was a hastle for me when you do your Tashania spell quest or other of your spell quests it will seem to make a difference.  <br>
