<br>
First, was the stein of moggok quest... being a dark elf, i should be able to do this quest at level 8, solo and with minimal fighting (if any, if i remember correctly)...  ended up still having to wait until the dog in the karanas was *just* this side of green.  no big deal, really, except that the 10 int boost is a nice one to start off with (being a non-twink, poo- 'chanter).  At 54 I still walk around with it. &gt;shrug&lt;  i'm strange though.<br>
<br>
The only other issues i've had, really, revolved around Firiona Vie outpost.  For my Illusion: Iksar spell, i had to hire the services of a high elf to do my final turn in and return the spell to me, but with that knowledge, i knew to begin committing mass genocide on the goblins in Warsilk's Woods until reaching 50, when i was able to walk in and speak to the epic NPC there.<br>
<br>
